**Post 3**

URL: https://www.linkedin.com/posts/ethanls_evaluation-critiques-of-ai-growth-study-activity-7439656854017839106-umVG

Content:
Evaluation is the hardest problem in AI right now.

Not building models.
Not prompting.

Evaluating them.

Most teams rely on:

Gut feel
Anecdotes
Cherry-picked examples

But that doesn’t scale.

What you actually need:
→ Clear evaluation frameworks
→ Defined success metrics
→ Repeatable testing

Because without evaluation,

you don’t know if you’re improving —

or just guessing.

